name: Heartseeker Lucian
description: Behind curtain one: a dashing man with an adventurous plan. It seems he'll only agree to dinner by lantern light, but you can bet his intentions are pure… it's Lucian, here to sweep you off your feet and into the daring life of a Heartseeker.
